dvdauthor: dvdauthor (Simple DVD Authoring Tools)
dvdauthor:
dvdauthor: A simple set of tools to help you author a DVD. The idea is to be 
dvdauthor: able to create menus, buttons, chapters, by taking an mpeg stream (as 
dvdauthor: created by mplex -f 8 from mjpegtools 1.6.0) and write it to DVD.
